    Gemini

    The Gemini neural network is a type of neural architecture designed for natural language processing (NLP) tasks, particularly for text classification and sentiment analysis.

    Gemini uses a combination of local and global features to capture information at different scales. This allows the model to learn both fine-grained and coarse-grained representations of the input text.

    ChatGPT

    ChatGPT is a type of artificial intelligence (AI) designed to generate human-like text responses to user input. It's a variant of the popular transformer architecture, specifically tailored for conversational AI applications.

    ChatGPT is based on the transformer architecture introduced in the paper "Attention Is All You Need" by Vaswani et al. in 2017.

    Copilot

    Copilot is a neural network-based AI model developed by GitHub and OpenAI that assists developers in writing code. It's a type of AI-powered coding companion that can help with tasks such as code completion, code review, and even generating entire functions or classes.

    Gemini ART

    Gemini is a type of neural network designed to generate images. It's a deep learning model that uses a combination of techniques from computer vision and natural language processing to produce high-quality images.

    Standard subscription, Standard+, Premuim and Business.

    STANDART

    Our Standard Subscription is an ideal choice for those who want to access the basic functions of our Voice Assistant with Neural Networks. With this subscription, you will get the following features:

    Schedules, Reminders, Notes, Part of Customization, ChatGPT4o. The price of a Standard subscription is 0 RUB/month, it's absolutely free. This is an affordable price for access to the powerful features of our bot.

    STANDART+

    Take your experience with our Mayson to the next level with a Standard+ subscription equipped with advanced neural networks. This subscription offers a number of advanced features and benefits that will dramatically change the way you interact with Mayson.

    All functions from the standard subscription + Sending welcome messages, automatic sending of emails by voice, sending messages to contacts in tg, an increased part of customization. The subscription price is 100 Rub/month

    PREMUIM

    Take your experience with our Mayson to the next level with our Premium subscription, powered by cutting-edge neural networks. With this exclusive upgrade, you'll gain access to advanced features and enhanced capabilities that will revolutionize the way you interact with our AI-driven platform.

    This subscription includes everything that was included in the Standard + subscription, but also: Gemini Neural Network, Full customization is open, The ability to add your own commands, a code for a unique Avatar is issued upon purchase. The subscription will cost 200 rub/month

    BUSINESS

    Our Premium subscription is designed for individuals who want to maximize their productivity, gain a competitive edge, and stay at the forefront of innovation. By upgrading to Premium, you'll:

    All the advantages of the previous subscription + All available Neural networks, the ability to manage finances, in the schedule - Expenses/Income. The subscription will cost 300 Rub/month
